sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Applicant
    participant FE as React SPA
    participant API as ResumeController
    participant AiSvc as AiService<br/>(NVIDIA LLM)
    participant MatchSvc as MatchingService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: — Parse Resume —

    User->>FE: Upload resume (text / image / PDF)
    FE->>API: POST /api/resume/parse<br/>Body: { ResumeText, ImageBase64, IsPdf }

    alt PDF file
        API->>API: ExtractTextFromPdfBytes()<br/>using UglyToad.PdfPig
    else Image file
        API->>API: Base64 encode image
    end

    API->>AiSvc: ParseResumeAsync(text)
    AiSvc->>AiSvc: Build prompt with resume content
    AiSvc->>AiSvc: POST to NVIDIA API<br/>model: moonshotai/kimi-k2.6
    AiSvc-->>API: ParsedResume{ Skills[], Seniority,<br/>ExperienceYears, Education[], Summary }

    API-->>FE: 200 OK — ParsedResume object
    FE-->>User: Display parsed skills,<br/>seniority, education

    Note over User,DB: — Get Job Recommendations —

    User->>FE: Click "Get Recommendations"
    FE->>API: POST /api/resume/recommendations<br/>Body: { ResumeText }

    API->>AiSvc: ParseResumeAsync(resumeText)
    AiSvc-->>API: ParsedResume

    API->>DB: Create temporary UserProfile<br/>with parsed skills
    API->>MatchSvc: GetTopMatches(profile, topN=10)
    MatchSvc->>DB: Get active jobs
    MatchSvc->>MatchSvc: Score each job<br/>(5-factor algorithm)
    MatchSvc-->>API: List<MatchedJobDto>

    API-->>FE: 200 OK — ParsedResume + MatchedJobDto list
    FE-->>User: Display recommendations<br/>with match scores

    Note over User,DB: — Generate Cover Letter —

    User->>FE: Click "Generate Cover Letter"
    FE->>API: POST /api/resume/cover-letter<br/>Body: { JobTitle, CompanyName,<br/>JobDescription, Tone }
    API->>AiSvc: GenerateCoverLetterAsync(...)
    AiSvc->>AiSvc: POST to NVIDIA API
    AiSvc-->>API: CoverLetterResponse{ CoverLetter, Tips }
    API-->>FE: 200 OK — Cover letter + tips
    FE-->>User: Display cover letter<br/>with copy button
